  "title": "QC Inspector (Warehouse / Logistics)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure finished goods comply with customer-specified drawing specifications.</li>\n  <li>Conduct quality inspections for incoming and outgoing deliveries to verify conformance to specifications.</li>\n  <li>Perform dimensional, functional, and other tests using designated measuring equipment, test tools, or checklists.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and ensure timely fulfillment of scheduled deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Identify and isolate defective products, reporting and highlighting any variances or defects.</li>\n  <li>Conduct continuous in-process quality control checks on warehouse floor crates.</li>\n  <li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties assigned by the superior.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
